text: Jakub Wrąbel (born 8 June 1996) is a Polish footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Stal Mielec on loan from Wisla Plock. ==External links== * * ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Polish footballers Category:Poland under-21 international footballers Category:Ekstraklasa players Category:I liga players Category:Śląsk Wrocław players Category:Olimpia Grudziądz players Category:Wisła Płock players Category:Stal Mielec players Category:Sportspeople from Wrocław
